    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Objects originally created to cover or adorn a window, door, or doorway. This class does not include relatively permanent structural parts of buildings such as canopies, exterior shutters, and window sashes.</Note_Text>
